level.heading: Nonprofit housing developments - Submission of willful false statements.
History
level.text: (June 4, 1982, D.C. Law 4-112, § 8, 29 DCR 1687; repealed pursuant to § 305 of D.C. Law 11-111.)

level.heading: Legislative History of Law 11-111
level.text: For legislative history of D.C. Law 11-111, see Historical and Statutory Notes following § 34-2413.01.

level.heading: Editor's Notes
level.text: Repeal effective 90 days after meeting of Board: Section 305 of D.C. Law 11-111 repealed this section. However, § 601 of D.C. Law 11-111 provided that title III of the act shall apply 90 days after the initial meeting of the Board established by section 204 of the act.
